==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Guan
<hw>Guan</hw> <pr>(gw⟦aum⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>((Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of many species of large gallinaceous birds of Central and
South America, belonging to <gen>Penelope</gen>, <gen>Pipile</gen>,
<gen>Ortalis</gen>, and allied genera. Several of the species are often
domesticated.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Guana</ent>⟦br⟧
